Title: World Malaria Day
Narrative:
It's not an option but a necessity to keep the world safe and clean!

Let World Malaria Day remind us the need to educate masses about the life threatening diseases spread by mosquitoes & their prevention techniques.

Do you know?
Malaria can pass from human to human. You cannot “catch” malaria like you can a cold, but people can pass it on by sharing needles, blood transfusions and through pregnancy.
